{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 102705, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "tochaa", "body": "This is the final boss of BRD. Relatively hard for a group his level, however if your group is cooperative and alert you should be able to take him down fairly easily.\r\n\r\nFair warning would to be to clear all adds in the room. They will aggro if you do not kill them. This includes the adds on the top of stairways as well. \r\n\r\nThe princess, (http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=8929) who stands right beside him, is immune to sap and sheep.\r\n\r\nGood luck :)", "date": "2007-06-11T21:26:39-05:00", "rating": 42, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "The princess http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=8929 can, however, be shackled.  Do this if anybody in your group is doing the quest http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=4003 (Horde) or http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=4362 (Alliance), as those quests require that the princess stays alive throughout the battle.    If nobody has the quest, feel free to kill her, although she will help the Emperor during the battle.", "creationdate": "2007-07-05T22:04:39-05:00", "id": 304162, "rating": 3, "commentid": 102705, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "40787", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
