{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 160325, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "83140", "body": "Unforuneatly no-one around this instances level even knows who he is they think that flamelash is te last boss and i say \"no dagran is\" good luck finding a group for him\r\nTIP: best if the rogues stealth and kill the flamekeepers and light torches so the group can get through\r\nTIP 2: HIGH LEVEL ROGUES! or feral druids", "date": "2007-09-29T12:37:06-05:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "it is hard to find good group (58-60) for this boss since tbc... all 58 lvl players are moving to outland and ramp instance... so pre tbc 5-man end game instances are dead now (strat, scholo, lbrs, brd emperor run, dm) at least on my server... anyway my favorite instance (stratholme) is comming back in WoTLK as one of the Caverns of Time instance :)", "creationdate": "2007-10-06T16:57:32-05:00", "id": 313031, "rating": 3, "commentid": 160325, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "26469", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
