{"commentv2": 1, "number": 13, "id": 336160, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Strathcona", "body": "The Emperor yells things out as you're clearing the room.  Finally when the room is clear he will yell:\r\n\r\n\"Thank you for clearing out those foolish senators.  Now prepare to meet your doom at the hands of Ragnaros' most powerful servant.\"\r\n\r\nThen you know it's safe to pull with no adds.", "date": "2008-07-25T16:16:36-05:00", "rating": 46, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "This is no longer necessary. He doesn't pull the room anymore.", "creationdate": "2012-01-07T20:23:55-06:00", "id": 505970, "rating": 9, "commentid": 336160, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Catriona", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 14, "id": 353654, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "193810", "body": "Do you have a tech to solo this guy as a frost mage ? I tried to burst him down without success because of his Avatar of Flame ability which he casts very often. I tried to kit him but it's very long and i run oom, and the princess casts a hot on him (i steal it but just when he's not in avatar form). I got 3 s2 pieces and the s2 staff but I couldn't manage to kill him.", "date": "2008-08-15T12:06:31-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
