{"commentv2": 1, "number": 18, "id": 551177, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "skiper", "body": "soloed as 65lvl subtilety-rogue.\r\nthe one difficult was the emperor himself and \"the seven\". I died while trying to kill 'em, and decided to swim in lava instead of fighting. \r\nthat worked. the golem giant before emperor and packs in his room are easy. just sap elite mobs and kill non-elite. they are 55-56 lvl.\r\n\r\nI killed emperor on the 2nd attempt. \r\nI'm not sure if it is possible to do by any other class on this level, but for rogue its a challenge , but not  impossible one.\r\nSo. I started with premeditation+garrote, ripture, evasion. got some combo points by dodging his attacks. then used evasion again, shadow dance, premeditation+garrot , etc. had to drink 1 healing potion. Anyway, I still got only 200 hp when Emperor died, and cheating death helped a lot :)", "date": "2009-01-07T09:08:41-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I soloed him with a level 65 protection paladin.", "creationdate": "2009-01-25T12:21:59-06:00", "id": 383431, "rating": 0, "commentid": 551177, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "196309", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
