{"commentv2": 1, "number": 20, "id": 597337, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "159824", "body": "I could NOT solo him as a L73 fire mage, fairly poorly geared. The 10 second spell immunity is a crusher. I'll be back but not alone or not L73...\r\n\r\nCasters, beware.", "date": "2009-02-06T01:16:52-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
