{"commentv2": 1, "number": 42, "id": 1935562, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "1211863", "body": "I did not encounter the princess when trying to slay dagran. Instead a high priestess with somewhat 30k hp stand next to the boss. I guess it's because the quest royal rescue is obsolete. Funny that in game dungeon guide still list the existence of the princess and her abilities.", "date": "2014-01-18T08:31:56-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 16384, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 43, "id": 1962552, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Guanyin", "body": "I just got stunned for 40 seconds straight while soloing him on a level 56 Paladin. Broken mechanic much?", "date": "2014-05-01T21:51:58-05:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 44, "id": 2026344, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Ithuraen", "body": "Post stat-squish this guy hits like a freight train. Ran a LFG group and the level 55 warrior tank in heirloom gear, while I was a 60 paladin healer, yeah there is no way you're keeping a lower-level tank alive.\r\n\r\nThaurissian will happily hit for 1.5k every 1.5s or so, combined with his [url=http://wod.wowhead.com/spell=15636]Avatar of Flame[/url] ability dishing out an extra 300-400 per hit, finally combined with his Ironfoe meaning he can hit [b]four[/b] times with an extra 10% crit on each hit? [url=http://wod.wowhead.com/spell=17492]Did I mention he has a 5 second ranged stun on [i]no CD[/i] with [i]no diminshing returns[/i] that also [i]does damage[/i][/url]?\r\n\r\nIn short the tank pulled, took an Ironfoe hit right away and was left on 1k hp. I couldn't get a flash heal out before he took the next hit.\r\n\r\nWith very good 60 tank gear I could solo him (once respecced) thanks to not having to suffer his stuns. Otherwise quite a hard boss for LFG groups that range from level 51-60.", "date": "2014-11-08T09:08:49-06:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 45, "id": 2070964, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "braneman", "body": "If you have to farm this guy you can exit BRD quickly by jumping into molten core and then leaving molten core, it will take you back to the molten span instantly.", "date": "2014-12-17T08:03:18-06:00", "rating": 11, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "At this precise moment in time, due solely to the extraordinary helpfulness of your suggestion and my desire for [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=11930/the-emperors-new-cape]The Emperor's New Cape[/url], you are my favorite person in the multiverse.", "creationdate": "2015-02-12T16:50:21-06:00", "id": 839189, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2070964, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "beckiesuedalton", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 46, "id": 2295543, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "kalmus", "body": "Another guy who can be a real test of RNG - started farming again for Ironfoe on my paladin a few days ago. So far clocked in ~ 40 kills, grabbed his Family Jewels twice, and 3 black diamonds but no mace yet.\r\n \r\nHopefully tonight!", "date": "2016-01-06T12:43:50-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Finally got it on kill 124... proof that RNG really is random. At ~ 114 kills you are 99% likely to have seen a 4% drop rate item.", "creationdate": "2016-01-09T14:54:38-06:00", "id": 923912, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2295543, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "kalmus", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 47, "id": 2552769, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "precise", "body": "I hope Blizzard never nerfs this NPC. The final boss of vanilla's megadungeon should stay as brutal and epic as intended! Will give you a nice challenge as a healer that isn't insurmountable as long as you don't fall asleep when the tank takes high burst damage.", "date": "2018-02-14T23:44:16-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2018-02-14T23:52:10-06:00", 2, "precise"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 48, "id": 5155131, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Aldristavan", "body": "If you're farming BRD on live/retail and you're looking for a clear order:\r\n[ul]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9018/high-interrogator-gerstahn]Gerstahn[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9025/lord-roccor]Roccor[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9319/houndmaster-grebmar]Grebmar[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=10096/high-justice-grimstone]Ring of Law[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9016/baelgar]Bael'Gar[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9017/lord-incendius]Lord Incendius[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9056/fineous-darkvire]Fineous Darkvire[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9033/general-angerforge]General Angerforge[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=8983/golem-lord-argelmach]Golem Lord Argelmach[/url][/li]\r\n[li]Grim Guzzler:[/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n[ol]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9537/hurley-blackbreath]Hurley Blackbreath[/url] (Go to the storeroom to your left and attack the three Thunderbrew Lager Kegs. This summons Hurley Blackbreath.)[/li]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9543/ribbly-screwspigot]Ribbly Screwspigot[/url] (Talk to Ribbly Screwspigot. Click on the only dialog option. Kill him and his goons.)[/li]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9502/phalanx]Phalanx[/url] (Buy 6 Dark Iron Ale Mugs from Plugger Spazzring. Turn them in to Private Rocknot. He will then move towards the kegs and break them open. This starts a riot and turns Phalanx hostile. Kill Phalanx.[/li]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9499/plugger-spazzring]Plugger Spazzring[/url] (after Phalanx)[/li]\r\n[/ol][ul]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9156/ambassador-flamelash]Ambassador Flamelash[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/object=169243/chest-of-the-seven]Trial of the Seven[/url][/li]\r\n[/ul]\r\n(Before heading into the Lyceum, take the Molten Bridge to the right if you're a completionist and you're doing [url=https://www.wowhead.com/quest=7848/attunement-to-the-core][Attunement to the Core][/url])\r\n[ul]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9938/magmus]Magmus[/url][/li]\r\n[li][url=https://www.wowhead.com/npc=9019/emperor-dagran-thaurissan]Emperor Dagran Thaurissan[/url][/li]\r\n[/ul]", "date": "2021-04-18T03:04:39-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": false, "beta": false}}